2005-01-31  Ralf Wildenhues  <Ralf.Wildenhues@gmx.de>

	* m4/libtool.m4 (_LT_CMD_GLOBAL_SYMBOLS): Unicos 9 sed rejects
	empty parentheses as in 's/x\(\)/\1/'.
